       [-quiet]

       Displays  the following information about the specified setSIMode para-
       meters in the Innovus log file and the Innovus console:

              * Parameter name

              * Current value

              * Type (Boolean, string, and so on)

              * Whether the current value was set by user

       If you do not specify any parameters, the software displays information
       for all of the parameters.

Parameters
       <parameter_names>
              Displays information for the specified parameters. You can spec-
              ify one or more parameters.

              See setSIMode for descriptions of the parameters you  can  spec-
              ify.

       -quiet Displays  the  current  settings for the specified parameters in
              Tcl list format only.

              If you specify -quiet without any parameters, the software  dis-
              plays  the  current  settings of all the setSIMode parameters in
              Tcl list format.

Examples
              * The following command displays the current setting of the -an-
                alyzeNoiseThreshold, and -deltaDelayThreshold parameters:

                getSIMode -analyzeNoiseThreshold -deltaDelayThreshold

                The software displays the following information:

                -analyzeNoiseThreshold 20 # int, default=20

                -deltaDelayThreshold -1 # float, default=-1

                {analyzeNoiseThreshold 20} {deltaDelayThreshold -1}

              * The following command displays the current  settings  for  all
                setSIMode parameters in Tcl list format only:

                getSIMode -quiet

                The software displays the following information:

                {acceptableWNS   same}  {analyzeNoiseThreshold  20}  {deltaDe-
                layThreshold -1} {insCeltICPostTcl  {}}  {insCeltICPreTcl  {}}
                {maxNrIter  2}  {noiseTwfMode  {}}  {targetPathGroups {reg2reg
                in2out  in2reg  reg2out}}   {usePrevCeltICRunDir   {}{vaDecou-
                pleThreshold 10} {vaThreshold 15} {vaMode cap}}

